Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.25,0:28:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我还没看耶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.31,0:28:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.63,0:28:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快点的话\N我们会到外太空去的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.40,0:28:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,门一开　我们就往外跳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.76,0:29:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你绝对不可以放手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.10,0:29:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.40,0:29:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要开囉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.44,0:29:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.28,0:29:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你奸诈狡猾又冷酷无情
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.34,0:30:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是永远孤零零一个人\N也太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The Paper　听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.41,0:30:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.12,0:30:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战结果呢　伟人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.21,0:30:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经被我歼灭了　任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.20,0:30:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好　The Paper
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.36,0:30:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上派人过去接你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.28,0:30:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.70,0:30:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.49,0:31:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(请照顾我妹妹)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.07,0:31:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南西…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.51,0:31:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是裘克
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.32,0:31:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好　我是读子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.78,0:31:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见了\N产假老师的工作如何
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.46,0:31:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经结束了\N我有一件事想请问你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南西她现在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.89,0:31:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在医疗看护所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.02,0:31:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她当时脑部缺氧\N所以记忆倒退了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.98,0:31:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,治得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.03,0:31:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前为她进行了严厉的\N短期学习处理才好了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.91,0:31:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过她现在这样比较幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.15,0:32:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是恢复了\N就要接受法律裁决了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.68,0:32:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我跟她见面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.43,0:32:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.47,0:32:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借给我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.38,0:33:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.48,0:33:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姊姊　你是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.23,0:33:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫读子．利德曼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.38,0:33:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你姊姊的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.80,0:33:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有姊姊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.48,0:33:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呀　不过已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.00,0:33:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很坚强很和善
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.86,0:33:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一个拯救了世界的杰出女性
